463\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Bees.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-324 aligncenter\" title=\"Up close with a frame\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Bees-620x463.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"463\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/BeesCloseup.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-325 aligncenter\" title=\"Close up of our bees\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/BeesCloseup-620x463.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"463\" />\r\n</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHappy, healthy bees!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Our Apiary is Expanding!','','publish','open','open','','chugs-apiary-is-expanding','','','2013-07-19 13:37:06','2013-07-19 12:37:06','',0,'http://chug.org.uk/?p=296',0,'post','',0),(297,1,'2013-06-20 23:05:39','2013-06-20 22:05:39','<a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0676.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-289\" title=\"Cakes at our open day\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0676-620x413.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" /></a><a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0689.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-290\" title=\"Cakes\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0689-620x413.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" /></a><a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0786.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-292\" title=\"4X7V0786\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0786-620x413.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" /></a><a href=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0775.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-291\" title=\"4X7V0775\" src=\"http://chug.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4X7V0775-620x413.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" /></